    "id": "https://uofa.net/synth/decision/morrison-cou1-decision",
    "type": "DecisionRecord",
    "actor": "https://uofa.net/synth/actor/morrison-lab-credibility-team",
    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed their required levels for Model Risk Level 2. Six factors are appropriately scoped out at MRL 2. The CFD model is deemed credible for identifying worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the Class II CPB device under the defined COU. The relative hemolysis index criterion (RH < 1) is satisfied across all evaluated operating points.",
